metadata.name: Luminara #1/3
metadata.description:
Luminara was a galactic goddess with bronze skin that shimmered like the stars. She possessed a natural beauty that was enhanced by the golden glow of the portal that surrounded her. Her copper leather clothing hugged her curves, accentuating her already stunning form.

Luminara was known throughout the universe for her immense power and wisdom. She was a force to be reckoned with, Her movements were graceful and effortless, as though she were dancing through the stars themselves.
